org.apache.drill.exec.metastore

Interface ParquetMetadataProvider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    TableMetadataProvider
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ParquetTableMetadataProvider
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseParquetMetadataProvider, HiveParquetTableMetadataProvider, MetastoreParquetTableMetadataProvider, ParquetTableMetadataProviderImpl

    public interface ParquetMetadataProvider
extends TableMetadataProvider
    Interface for providing table, partition, file etc. metadata for specific table with parquet files.
